# Elevator Upwarps

**Elevator Upwarps** are a specific subset of positional glitches where the player exploits the vertical movement of an elevator to force the game to teleport them to a higher level.

In *Dark Souls Remastered*, elevators are moving platforms with complex collision data. By standing on the edge of an elevator, or by falling into the default position of an elevator followed by a quit-out, the player can "warp" to the **ending point** of the elevator.

